Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.80,0:00:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，好清爽的天空唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.39,0:00:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遠足的好日子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.73,0:00:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時放馬過來吧，暗妖精!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.42,0:00:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護妮絲和餅乾平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.73,0:00:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要成為一個\N獨單一面的騎士!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.67,0:00:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史派克，過來一起吃午飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.84,0:00:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這梅干好好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.08,0:00:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉，我的任務到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.68,0:00:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有史派克喜歡的柴魚口味喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.98,0:00:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔，真的嗎?我馬上去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.42,0:00:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴魚柴魚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.52,0:00:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要開動囉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.29,0:00:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大魚大魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.99,0:00:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一竿釣上的餅乾，我拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.89,0:00:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，餅乾小偷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.36,0:00:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，別來妨礙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.26,0:00:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是重要的貨物，不交給你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.60,0:00:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，放手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.05,0:00:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.90,0:01:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你放手就放手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.37,0:01:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要就是不要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.65,0:01:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?今天的天氣預報說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.68,0:01:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴天偶有餅乾是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.12,0:01:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，為什麼都被牠吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.17,0:01:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾、狡猾、太狡猾了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.73,0:01:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…最重要的餅乾…\N我的騎士夢想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.86,0:01:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不關我的事~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.77,0:01:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.40,0:01:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明才剛進入新系列的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.30,0:01:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去我會\N一直只是個見習騎士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.71,0:01:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?這香味是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.47,0:01:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火候剛剛好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.38,0:01:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也真是方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.05,0:01:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有材料和龍寶寶\N要烤多少餅乾都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝龍寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.15,0:01:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要烤多少都可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.79,0:01:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的任務…究竟\N算什麼…可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.98,0:01:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看哦
